# YapApp

YapApp is a real-time chat application built with Next.js, TailwindCSS, Zustand, Redis, and Pusher.
It supports secure Google authentication and features dynamic chat pages, message storage, and real-time updates.

## 🚀 Live Demo

https://yapapp.vercel.app

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Frontend**: Next.js (App Router), TailwindCSS, DaisyUI, Zustand
- **Backend**: Server Actions, Redis (Upstash), Pusher, Auth.js

## 🔐 Features

- Google Sign-In with Auth.js
- Real-time messaging using Pusher
- Redis for message storage
- Zustand for client state management
- Responsive UI with light/dark mode
- Push notifications (in progress)

## 📦 Installation

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/yapapp
cd yapapp
npm install
npm run dev
